---
layout: layouts/base.njk
pageTitle: Clash Verge Tags 内容索引
description: 通过 Tags 快速查看 Clash Verge 相关主题内容。
permalink: /tags/
---
<main class="light-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow" style="color:#0f5db8;">Tags</p>
        <h1 class="page-title-white">Clash Verge Tags 内容索引</h1>
        <p>按系统、功能与使用场景整理文章入口。</p>
      </div>
      <a class="soft-button" style="color:#152033;" href="/blog/">博客列表</a>
    </div>
    <div class="tag-grid">
      {% for tag in collections.tagList %}
      <a class="tag-card" href="{{ tag | tagUrl }}">
        <strong>{{ tag }}</strong>
        <span>查看相关内容</span>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
